introducing collection 001 : perfectly provocative
available for preorder november 10 at 9 am pdt.

creative direction/videographer : @laurensoyung 
models : @yuzzzzt @heart200bpm @mzolagrinta 
mua : @brookelturnbull

the past 2 years i've spent learning, sampling, designing, and developing SOYUNG between LA and London. amidst all the tears, frustrations, & laughs, i am proud to present my debut collection:
Perfectly Provocative.

throughout my journey, i've gained the most from trial & error. for me, starting was the hardest part because i had no clue where to begin. not being someone from a traditional background of design, i felt like an imposter, especially being surrounded by csm graduates all over london lol. i also played various roles. i was not only the designer, but the pattern cutter, photographer, graphic designer, among others (PS in 2024 we are looking to hire so be on the lookout ;))

to show you where my head was at throughout all this, is a glimpse into the developmental process. taking my sketches and bringing it to life!

it was also extremely important to me to have SOYUNG be a 100% eco-friendly and sustainable brand. all of the pieces are ethically produced in a studio by a small team in London and are MADE TO ORDER so that there is 0 WASTE to ensure the reduction of environmental impacts.

building SOYUNG was the most challenging yet most rewarding dream to achieve in the world. an immense thank you to all the beautiful humans that have trusted and believed in me throughout this journey and offered me their guidance.

but this is just beginning! there is so much i have in the works that i cannot wait to share with all of you!!! but in the meantime, go treat yourself, your girlfriend, friend, mom, aunt, niece, sister, daughter, whoever by buying a SOYUNG piece. (P.S. unisex pieces are also otw ;) ) @soyungofficial is now LIVE!!!

xx,
Lauren SoYung
